---
<section class="dark-about">
  <div class="dark-about-inner">
    <p class="da-label">About me</p>
    <h2 class="da-heading">Architecture, AI,<br/>and engineering rigor.</h2>
    <p class="da-sub">I'm João Pster, a senior software engineer and AI engineer with 6+ years building products. Today I'm co-founding an AI-driven platform for the US real-estate market, and I'm the one writing the code. I build software that scales and stays maintainable, shipped fast without trading away quality, and I use AI the right way: with specs, tests, and review, not vibes.</p>
    <div class="da-grid">
      <div class="da-card">
        <div class="da-icon">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
            <path d="M5 6l4 3-4 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M10 12h3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Architecture &amp; engineering</h3>
        <p>Full-stack systems built to last. TypeScript end to end, NestJS on the server, Angular and React on the front, all with clear boundaries, typed contracts, and tests that actually run. Boring in the best way.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/J-Pster" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="da-link">See my work on GitHub →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="da-card">
        <div class="da-icon">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
            <circle cx="9" cy="9" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            <path d="M9 1v2M9 15v2M1 9h2M15 9h2M3.5 3.5l1.4 1.4M13.1 13.1l1.4 1.4M14.5 3.5l-1.4 1.4M4.9 13.1l-1.4 1.4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>AI engineering</h3>
        <p>I do spec-driven development with AI: phased, documented, and reviewed, the way I build any software. Engineering rigor over one-shot prompts, with tests and review on every line, in any stack.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/J-Pster/Psters_AI_Workflow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="da-link">Explore the AI Workflow →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dark-about {
    background: var(--color-surface-dark);
    padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-xl);
  }
  .dark-about-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .da-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.88px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .da-heading { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-on-dark); letter-spacing: -1.44px; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .da-sub { font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: var(--space-xxl); }
  .da-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-base); }
  .da-card { background: var(--color-surface-dark-elevated); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-lg); }
  .da-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: var(--radius-md); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .da-card h3 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-on-dark); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .da-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-on-dark-soft); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .da-card p strong { color: var(--color-on-dark); font-weight: 600; }
  .da-link { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: #47c2ff; text-decoration: none; }
  .da-link:hover { opacity: 0.8; text-decoration: none; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .da-heading { font-size: 36px; } .da-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .dark-about { padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-base); } .da-heading { font-size: 28px; } }
</style>
